{"tid":1331741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721 勉勵] 各位，我哋係有選擇","createTime":"2019-07-19T05:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T14:26:27.000Z","uid":26332,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"298521244361d21b818db67e0ef749faa5fd6b7e","tid":1331741,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.magicalquote.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/If-you-dont-like-how-the-table-is-set-turn-over-the-table.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.magicalquote.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F01%2FIf-you-dont-like-how-the-table-is-set-turn-over-the-table.jpg&h=5a0dc687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/231237_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F231237_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=f76bc8e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\nIf you don't like how the table is set, turn over the table<br />\n如果你唔鐘意個局嘅擺法，請反枱！</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果721後仆街政府無回應，中聯辦以至中央班大陸喱繼續插手香港事務，要香港巿民行大陸個套垃圾思維制度，我哋係有選擇，就係反枱！！！</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>學侵侵咁lor，你唔回應訴求？OK：</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/iwI48nt0sqgkU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FiwI48nt0sqgkU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=1925a9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>721 後，5大訴求仍然難以達成？<br />\nOK無問題！忘記個5大訴求！<br />\n到時會只有1個訴求：<ins>香港獨立！</ins></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人絕不屈服！<br />\n各位唔洗怕！不要退縮！<br />\n對方越強硬，我哋越強大！<br />\n721 見！</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"cbafcc7170cc2cb4e828bf405a654185f6b74fbd","tid":1331741,"uid":2612,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGem6Rf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGem6Rf.png&h=b24b8c13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5pY84L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5pY84L.png&h=3ded51ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mijY84T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmijY84T.png&h=82615ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa126e05af31c1600f822327946b5d514d9cf44","tid":1331741,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"828e0ac31ac8eccb81a5a2d04a0b105faebf3af7","tid":1331741,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"puish"},{"pid":"5569d16fdd86d72ab1d2fe463d551483ae32d6d7","tid":1331741,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:05:46.000Z","msg":"【\b721文宣】星期日前一齊做鍵盤戰士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327641</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXAdLRx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXAdLRx.jpg&h=988ba3dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aw6P3Dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faw6P3Dd.jpg&h=545a2bea&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxBsQid.jpg\" data-thumbna