font-size: large;\"><br />\nIf you don't like how the table is set, turn over the table<br />\n如果你唔鐘意個局嘅擺法，請反枱！</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果721後仆街政府無回應，中聯辦以至中央班大陸喱繼續插手香港事務，要香港巿民行大陸個套垃圾思維制度，我哋係有選擇，就係反枱！！！</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>學侵侵咁lor，你唔回應訴求？OK：</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/iwI48nt0sqgkU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FiwI48nt0sqgkU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=1925a9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>721 後，5大訴求仍然難以達成？<br />\nOK無問題！忘記個5大訴求！<br />\n到時會只有1個訴求：<ins>香港獨立！</ins></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人絕不屈服！<br />\n各位唔洗怕！不要退縮！<br />\n對方越強硬，我哋越強大！<br />\n721 見！</span></span></strong></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"721 我放棄啦 大家都忘記左媽媽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331802</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e9b9a6642256f9b0c2d7a7bc7b91fc21d14b31a","tid":1331741,"uid":264697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:42:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d544c9771dcf7af67a044fd6b9451a9ffa192d86","tid":1331741,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:44:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2d4199e6d129968f483b2b03eb5f1328485f2fb","tid":1331741,"uid":123274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"14966042a0808a45308b48d99d0093d651966033","tid":1331741,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"8a86982ccab59ccdfc5483a1a5f31a1d896acd4b","tid":1331741,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:48:05.000Z",